data.description: This unique country property sits on 1 acre of highly improved late and boasts a refinished 3 bedroom/2 bath home - just waiting for a family! Have the benefits of living out of the city limits, all while having the convenience of living in town! Spend Summer nights outdoors by the fire pit or in the outdoor shop! This home has an attached, and very large, 2 car carport that is easily accessible by the ramp to the inside! Inside, there is a large kitchen, full of cabinets, to go with a large, light and roomy, living room - perfect for guests! This property is country living at its finest!
